    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>No. 573
                    The Ambassador in Italy
                     (
                        Kirk
                    ) to the Acting Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945Berlinv01</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d573</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">573</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-06-26T17:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-06-26T17:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-06-26T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-06-26T17:00:00-05:00" n="573" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d573">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Control (<persName corresp="#p_I2">Italy</persName>)/6–2745: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 573<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in <persName corresp="#p_I2">Italy</persName>
                    </hi> (<persName corresp="#p_KMGNJ1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kirk</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Caserta</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-06-27T00:00:00+02:00">June 27, 1945—midnight</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2794. …</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . .</p>
                <p>When we asked <gloss target="#t_SAC1">SAC</gloss> his view as to Yugo reservation
                    on art 3 of Belg[rade] Agreement he expressed concurrence with our view that on
                    this point [we] must stand. He then commented: “Please do not worry about civil
                        <gloss target="#t_admin1">admin</gloss> in our area. As you know the Bel
                    Agreement gives me final author in the matter and I shall see to it that the
                    interpretation is such as to represent our views”.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_KMGNJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Kirk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
